document_data.Notable Owners:
* [[Duvan]], a [[rogue]] that operated in [[Sespech]], carried around twin stilettos in his thigh scabbards.
* [[Iahn Qoyllor]], a [[Deep Imaskari]] [[Imaskari vengeance taker|vengeance taker]], wielded a stiletto with a [[lyrwood]] handle during his quest to apprehend [[Ususi Manaallin]] in early {{yearlink|1374}}.{{cite book/Darkvision|4|1}}
* [[Morris]], a [[Ravenian]] [[ranger]] that was trained in fighting with stilettos.{{Cite polyhedron/72/The Living City: Swimming Lessons|6-7}}
* [[Scoril Cimber]], a renowned [[Cormyrean]] highwayman, kept a stiletto concealed within his boots.
* [[Sheenra Duth]] carried four stilettos on her person.
* [[Tekuna Chand]], an [[assassin]] that wielded a magical stiletto.{{cite book/Desert of Desolation|14}}
* [[Urdek]], a bandit in [[Phlan]].
* [[Yys Fech]], a member of [[Spath Investigations]] and a former thief, was proficient in fighting with stilettos.<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/104/Spath Investigations|24}}
